<html><head><style>body{font-family:'Segoe UI', Calibri, sans-serif; line-height:1.6;} h1{color:#2E4053; border-bottom:2px solid #2E4053;} h2{color:#2874A6;} code{background:#F4F6F6; padding:2px; font-family:Consolas, monospace;}</style></head><body><h1>HTML Template: activity_enrollments.html</h1>
<h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>
<p>Defines the structural layout and content for a specific web page view.</p>
<h2>2. Code Logic &amp; Functionality</h2>
<p>Uses the Jinja2 templating engine. The file allows for dynamic data insertion using <code>{{ variable }}</code> syntax and control structures like <code>{% if %}</code> loops within standard HTML markup.</p>
<h2>3. Key Concepts &amp; Definitions</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Jinja2</strong>: A modern and designer-friendly templating language for Python.</li>
<li><strong>Template Inheritance</strong>: The ability to extend a base layout (<code>base.html</code>) to avoid code duplication.</li>
<li><strong>DOM</strong>: Document Object Model, the data representation of the objects that comprise the structure and content of a document on the web.</li>
</ul>
<h2>4. Location Details</h2>
<p><strong>Path</strong>: <code>templates\admin\activity_enrollments.html</code>
<strong>Type</strong>: .HTML File</p>
<h2>5. Source Code Preview (Snippet)</h2>
<p>Running typical software analysis on this file:</p>
<p>```html
{% extends "base.html" %}</p>
<p>{% block title %}{{ activity.name }} - Enrollments{% endblock %}</p>
<p>{% block content %}</p>
<div class="container py-5">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
        <div>
            <h2 class="mb-1"><i class="fas fa-user-friends me-2 text-primary"></i>{{ activity.name }} - Enrollments</h2>
            <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                <span class="badge bg-secondary">{{ activity.day_of_week }}</span>
                {{ activity.start_time }} - {{ activity.end_time }}
            </p>
        </div>
        <a href="{{ url_for('admin_dashboard') }}" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>Back to Dashboard
        </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Row -->
    <div class="row g-4 mb-4">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-users fa-2x mb-3 text-success"></i>
                    <h3 class="mb-0">{{ total_enrolled }}</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Enrolled Students</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-chair fa-2x mb-3 text-info"></i>
                    <h3 class="mb-0">{{ available_spots }}</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Available Spots</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-table-cells fa-2x mb-3 text-warning"></i>
                    <h3 class="mb-0">{{ activity.max_capacity }}</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Total Capacity</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-pound-sign fa-2x mb-3 text-primary"></i>
                    <h3 class="mb-0">Â£{{ "%.2f"|format(activity.price * total_enrolled) }}</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Total Revenue</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Enrolled Students List -->
    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white py-3">
            <h5 class="mb-0"><i class="fas fa-list me-2"></i>Enrolled Students ({{ total_enrolled }})</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body p-0">
            {% if enrollment_data %}
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-hover mb-0">
                    <thead class="table-light">
                        <tr>
                            <th>Student</th>
                            <th>Year Group</th>
                            <th>Parent/Guardian</th>
                            <th>Contact</th>
                            <th>Booking Date</th>
                            <th>Status</th>
                            <th>Actions</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for data in enrollment_data %}
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                    <div class="avatar bg-success text-white rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center me-2"
                                        style="width: 35px; height: 35px; font-size: 14px;">
                                        {{ data.child.name[0] }}
                                    </div>
                                    <strong>{{ data.child.name }}</strong>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="badge bg-info">Year {{ data.child.grade }}</span>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <strong>{{ data.parent.full_name }}</strong>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <small class="text-muted">
                                    <i class="fas fa-envelope me-1"></i>{{ data.parent.email }}<br>
                                    <i class="fas fa-phone me-1"></i>{{ data.parent.phone if data.parent.phone else
                                    'N/A' }}
                                </small>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <small>{{ data.booking.booking_date.strftime('%d %b %Y') }}</small>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                {% if data.booking.status == 'confirmed' %}
                                <span class="badge bg-success">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-1"></i>Confirmed
                                </span>
                                {% else %}
                                <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark">
                                    {{ data.booking.status|title }}
                                </span>
                                {% endif %}
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <form action="{{ url_for('admin_cancel_booking', booking_id=data.booking.id) }}"
                                    method="POST" style="display: inline;"
                                    onsubmit="return confirm('Are you sure you want to cancel this booking for {{ data.child.name }}? Notifications will be sent to the parent and tutor.');">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="csrf_token" value="{{ csrf_token() }}">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-danger" title="Cancel Booking">
                                        <i class="fas fa-times-circle me-1"></i>Cancel
                                    </button>
                                </form>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            {% else %}
            <div class="p-5 text-center text-muted">
                <i class="fas fa-inbox fa-4x mb-3 opacity-50"></i>
                <h5>No Enrollments Yet</h5>
                <p class="mb-0">This activity has no enrolled students at the moment.</p>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>

    {% if enrollment_data %}
    <!-- Additional Information -->
    <div class="alert alert-info mt-4" role="alert">
        <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
        <strong>Note:</strong> Cancelling a booking from here will send automatic email notifications to the parent and
        the assigned tutor.
        Any students on the waitlist will be automatically promoted.
    </div>
    {% endif %}
</div>

<style>
    .avatar {
        font-weight: bold;
    }
</style>
<p>{% endblock %}
```</p></body></html>